{"tid":2113941,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[東網] 新冠肺炎中年男性高危 專家指病毒有「7怕」 籲8招提高免疫力","createTime":"2020-07-18T12:25:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-18T12:54:15.000Z","uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a8fd69dd5933d785532e9d7c4f17eb5ea7274556","tid":2113941,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T12:25:10.000Z","msg":"[東網] 新冠肺炎中年男性高危 專家指病毒有「7怕」 籲8招提高免疫力<br />\n07月18日(六) 20:02更新<br />\n<br />\n&quot;有專家分析，新冠肺炎病毒有「7怕」，包括害怕紫外線、攝氏56度以上高溫、空氣流通、含氯消毒劑、75%濃度酒精、勤洗手、以及人體免疫力。該專家同時提出8項提升免疫力的方法，包括充足睡眠、早餐多吃乳酪、多吃洋蔥和大蒜、常飲蜂蜜水及檸檬水、多補充維他命C、堅持鍛煉身體、多曬太陽、以及保持微笑和樂觀開朗。 &quot;"},{"pid":"e2f0b346a38ed3a14eb7b03c3fd90f30c6fee244","tid":2113941,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T12:26:31.000Z","msg":"因為啲唔戴口罩嘅都係死啊伯較多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a5e0b013cbb907b97afc4945d65854bed139f2a","tid":2113941,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T12:28:01.000Z","msg":"早餐多吃乳酪、多吃洋蔥和大蒜<br />\n<br />\n但咁食法<br />\n啲屎一定好臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d51b442e7d2007f6aa940e0e05a35cf8109ef6c","tid":2113941,"uid":259088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T12:28:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e698676a7d5bfacfeb48dbdcf29d7ce7aaca842c","tid":2113941,"uid":346806,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7a5e0b013cbb907b97afc4945d65854bed139f2a","tid":2113941,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T12:28:01.000Z","msg":"早餐多吃乳酪、多吃洋蔥和大蒜<br />\n<br />\n但咁食法<br />\n啲屎一定好臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime"